        "reaction_type_english": "Hydrocracking reaction",
        "description": "在Pt/H-Mordenite和Pt/ZrO2(W)双功能催化剂上，对两种生物质基费托石蜡混合物（WAXA: C16-C46; WAXB: C11-C45）进行加氢裂化。反应在300-350°C、40 bar压力、H2/烃体积比600的条件下进行，液体空速(LHSV)在0.5-2.0 h⁻¹范围内变化。研究了C21+转化率以及气体、汽油、喷气燃料和柴油馏分的产率和组成。",
        "text_snippet": "Two biomass-based Fischer-Tropsch paraffins comprising of 16–46 and11–45carbon number range alkanes werehydrocrackedoverzeolitemordeniteandtungstated-zirconia-supportedplatinumcatalysts.Thereaction wascarriedoutinthetemperaturerangeof300–350°C,at40barpressureandhydrogen/hydrocarbonvolumeratioof600.Theliquidhourlyspacevelocitywasvariedintherangeof0.5and2.0h−1.",
